INT 2 1 H ; INT
STANDS
FOR INTERRUPT INTERRUPT NO
FOR DOS SERVICES
POP AX
CALL D I S P L A Y
MOV AH, 4CH INT 21H
INSTRUCTION
21H IS
DISPLAY PROC
NEAR : PROC IS KEYWORD FOR PROCEDURE
MOV CH, 04H MOV CL, 04H DISPI:
ROL AX, CL:
ROTATE LEFT 4 TIMES
PUSH A X : SAVING ON STACK
AND AL, OFH
AD AL, 30H; 48 NI DECIMAL
CMP AL, ' 9 ; COMPARE WITH ASCII VALUE OF 9
IBE DISP2
AD AL, 7
DISP2: MOV DL, LA
MOV AH, 02H INT 21H
POP AX DEC CH
INZ DISPI
RET
D I S P L A Y ENDP END
